Package functional.genericKeywords

Class GenericKeywords

java.lang.Object
functional.genericKeywords.ThreadLocalFunctionalities
functional.genericKeywords.GenericKeywords
All Implemented Interfaces:
GenericKeywordsInterface
Direct Known Subclasses:
FileUtilities, TestExecutionEngine
public class GenericKeywords extends ThreadLocalFunctionalities implements GenericKeywordsInterface
This class represents a set of generic keywords and utility methods used in automated testing. It provides common functionalities such as interacting with web elements, browser navigation, and logging. This class is designed to be extended and used in test automation frameworks.
